description:
The Killer is just off her upset victory over the veteran Jester. She is tall, strong and determined. The Killer is ready to prove she deserves the ranking she as achieved. She is currently ranked 6th after just 2 matches.
Rogue comes to the US mat for the first time, she is high spirited and feisty. She grew up with old brothers and is ready to throw down with anyone at US. You got to love spunk.
title: The Killer (1-1)
